---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — AgentleConsulting"
  description="AgentleConsulting Privacy Policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data.">

  <div class="bg-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-site max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl text-slate mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate/50 mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate/75 space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Who We Are</h2>
          <p>AgentleConsulting is a Dutch automation consultancy serving Amazon and Bol.com sellers across Europe. Registered in Amsterdam, Netherlands. VAT: NL0048.72.4.12.B.01.</p>
          <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@agentleconsulting.com" class="text-sage">hello@agentleconsulting.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide to us through our contact form, discovery call booking, or email correspondence:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Name and business name</li>
            <li>Email address and phone number</li>
            <li>Information about your Amazon/Bol.com business (order volume, platforms used, current workflows)</li>
            <li>Any other information you choose to share</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not collect payment information — all payments are processed through separate, PCI-compliant payment providers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide consultation services</li>
            <li>Schedule and conduct discovery calls</li>
            <li>Send you proposals and contractual documents</li>
            <li>Communicate about ongoing projects</li>
            <li>Send you blog posts and insights (only if you've opted in)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We never sell your data to third parties.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Cookies</h2>
          <p>Our website uses one functional cookie to store your cookie consent preference. No tracking or marketing cookies are set without your explicit consent.</p>
          <p>For more details, see our <a href="/legal/cookies" class="text-sage">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain contact form submissions for 24 months. Project-related data is retained for 7 years to comply with Dutch tax and commercial record-keeping requirements. You can request deletion of non-contractual data at any time.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to processing</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@agentleconsulting.com" class="text-sage">hello@agentleconsulting.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Calendly</strong> — for discovery call scheduling. <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sage">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — our hosting provider. <a href="https://netlify.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sage">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> (with consent) — for website traffic analysis. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sage">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy periodically. The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date. For significant changes, we will notify existing clients by email.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related questions or to submit a data subject request:</p>
          <p>
            <strong>AgentleConsulting</strong><br/>
            Amsterdam, Netherlands<br/>
            <a href="mailto:hello@agentleconsulting.com" class="text-sage">hello@agentleconsulting.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
